{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Shin Seiki Evangelion", "title_uuid": "cc3209cd-c119-4870-b06c-9a34f447db7e", "volume": "Shin Seiki Evangelion 7", "volume_uuid": "3ce05597-5f0f-46cb-a775-8e61db3710aa", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1290, "img_height": 1061, "blocks": [{"box": [173, 342, 264, 364], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["貞本義行"]}, {"box": [96, 350, 340, 695], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["２００２年、いよいよ四十路に突入で", "ある！", "１０年前、４０歳になったらさすがに", "「もー．．．もう少し大人になってるだろうと思う」", "ってたのに、なんだか、やっぱり精神", "年齢は２０代で仕まってるような．．．。", "午前８００〜１１月２６日、近所の本屋でアイドル写真集", "に両手をそえたまま固まっている老", "人を見た。「なんだこのシンイは・」", "と蔑視しつつも、２０年後の自分を見", "でいるような気がして恐くなり、その", "日は写真集を手に取らずそこを立ち", "去った。勝った！！老人に勝つたのだ。"]}, {"box": [498, 289, 783, 325], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["．．．男の子の"]}, {"box": [102, 681, 202, 699], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．その日だけ"]}, {"box": [18, 1008, 168, 1029], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["装飾。〈鹿住忠広＋ＢＥＥＡＮＯ"]}, {"box": [490, 924, 539, 948], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["漫画"]}, {"box": [495, 955, 768, 1029], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ＹＯＳＴＨＵＫＩＳＡＤＡＭＯＴＯ", "原作／ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1224, 136, 1283, 235], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["・新世紀"]}, {"box": [563, 909, 779, 967], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["まあ、", "自急"]}, {"box": [1215, 703, 1290, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["真本義行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1211, 1006, 1289, 1048], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ＫＣＡＩ２．７", "角川書店"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-001.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 709, "img_height": 1040, "blocks": [{"box": [27, 142, 224, 280], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["男の戦い", "Ｖｏｌｕｍｅ", "週末義行", "ＹｏｕＴｕｂｅＴｕｓｔｉｃｈの", "原作／ＧＡＮＡＸ－"]}, {"box": [313, 292, 334, 301], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["はい"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-002.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1437, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [], "img_path": "EVA7-003.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1447, "img_height": 1054, "blocks": [{"box": [11, 66, 33, 181], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["登場人物紹介"]}, {"box": [58, 110, 314, 194], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["本編の主人公１０年以上も", "の間、借金のおに預けられ", "て育つ。突然父・ゲンドウによりネルフに", "呼ばれエヴァのハイロットとなる。（１は"]}, {"box": [179, 216, 274, 238], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["葛城ミサト"]}, {"box": [61, 265, 315, 349], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ネルフ本語以外の今日はキャンペーン", "局第一課所属シンジの", "肌の上司にあたる。おおらかな性格でシン", "ジの数少ない理解者。花の独身．．．。（２５歳。"]}, {"box": [180, 372, 271, 395], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["碇ゲンドウ"]}, {"box": [63, 423, 317, 506], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ルフの服装品日金上官、任務", "在上主義で実の息子にも冷蔵はだが、レイに", "は不思議な思いやりを見せる。（４８歳"]}, {"box": [63, 422, 321, 505], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["シンジの実父。特務制限ネ"]}, {"box": [354, 197, 649, 738], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["米国の第２８部が消滅し、残されたエヴァ３９検をネルフが引き取る事になった。そのア", "ストパイロットーフォース・チルトレシンピンシンの親友・公開トウンが選ばれる。彼は", "妹の病気の治療を条件に引き受けるが、エヴァに乗る恐怖心を隠せずシンジに打ち明ける。", "シンシンは現状な気持ちのまま姿を勇気づける事しかできなかった。そして始まった記載天", "陰の心中東京が先生、シンジ達が出来するが、改善日様はなんと使徒に乗っ取られたよう", "後だった。シンジはトウンの柔った９号機を攻撃できず、必死に呼びかけるが逆にやられ", "でしょう。シンガ女撃てきないと見て取ったゲントウはダミーシステムに切り替える", "とんに攻撃を始める初夏機、シンジは最近にそれを止めようとするが容赦なく攻撃が効か", "く。そしてついに、シンジの目の前でよりこのあったエントリーブラグがつぶされてしまう", "い、３号線とトウンは完全に沈黙した．．．"]}, {"box": [666, 207, 690, 478], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["●前巻までのあらすじ"]}, {"box": [182, 524, 251, 551], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.5, "lines": ["．．．", "綾波レイ"]}, {"box": [61, 580, 318, 664], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["う以外の経歴は不明のお話の美少女、（１４歳）"]}, {"box": [64, 580, 317, 663], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["零号機のバイロットマル", "ドゥック機関の報告書によ", "って選ばれたファースト・チルドレンとい"]}, {"box": [182, 685, 292, 710], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["惣流・アスカ・"]}, {"box": [195, 712, 279, 727], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ラングレー"]}, {"box": [67, 721, 325, 822], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ドイツから来た弐号機のバ", "イロット。頭脳明新、操縦", "センス状態の完全無数のパーフェクト美少", "イベントマンルエディスク（世各リダト・（１４）"]}, {"box": [182, 839, 296, 869], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["加持リョウジ"]}, {"box": [66, 893, 319, 978], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ネルフ特殊監察部に所属し", "政府内務省の調査部員でも", "あるダブルスバイスパイ、ミナトの生徒代の恋", "人でアスカの植えの男性、「役員」"]}, {"box": [937, 156, 1225, 207], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＰＲＯＧＲＡＭ"]}, {"box": [998, 230, 1140, 248], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ＥｖＡＮＧＥＬＯＮ"]}, {"box": [856, 283, 1055, 308], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＭＥ：ハーフィスト"]}, {"box": [853, 491, 1037, 519], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＭＥＭの贖罪"]}, {"box": [849, 343, 1106, 449], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＮＥの灰色の空", "ＳＩＮＥでの雰問"]}, {"box": [850, 772, 1041, 806], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＥＥＲＯ消滅"]}, {"box": [853, 556, 1105, 594], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥ２５男の戦い"]}, {"box": [845, 614, 1134, 685], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＥＥＡＣ覚醒・前編", "前"]}, {"box": [853, 702, 1127, 736], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＭＥ７７覚醒－後編"]}, {"box": [1264, 264, 1326, 815], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["７ｄ４４なｇ７１２１１１６１"]}, {"box": [925, 839, 1043, 860], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["そんじゃイロした"]}, {"box": [1024, 925, 1201, 943], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ＫＡＴＳＬＰＡＧＩＮＥＡＴＯ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-004.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1444, "img_height": 1061, "blocks": [{"box": [442, 49, 670, 91], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＧＥＺＴフィスト"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-005.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1437, "img_height": 1054, "blocks": [{"box": [632, 84, 653, 148], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["だめです"]}, {"box": [75, 192, 148, 321], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["初号機のたとうかい？", "連動回路", "カットされました"]}, {"box": [649, 369, 672, 460], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["射出信号は？"]}, {"box": [319, 369, 368, 509], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ブラグ側から", "ロックされています"]}, {"box": [84, 383, 109, 475], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["受信しません"]}, {"box": [628, 595, 682, 788], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["シンジ君", "聞こえるか？バカなことは"]}, {"box": [610, 691, 625, 756], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["よすんだ"]}, {"box": [317, 620, 386, 732], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ああしなければ", "君がやられて", "いたんだぞ"]}, {"box": [238, 607, 279, 701], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["そんなこと", "わかってるよ"]}, {"box": [180, 854, 197, 893], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["でも"]}, {"box": [67, 954, 103, 1003], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["僕は"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-006.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1437, "img_height": 1064, "blocks": [{"box": [1314, 43, 1376, 188], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["その方が", "よかったんだ！！"]}, {"box": [1312, 637, 1376, 748], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["何を", "する気だ！？"]}, {"box": [870, 825, 896, 891], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["まずい"]}, {"box": [797, 882, 851, 1012], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["予備動力終了", "まで１分強"]}, {"box": [583, 46, 673, 200], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["・ごめんじゃない"]}, {"box": [178, 98, 225, 223], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ＬＣＬ圧縮濃度を", "限界まで上げろ！！"]}, {"box": [651, 564, 676, 588], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["は"]}, {"box": [477, 568, 505, 613], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["はい"]}, {"box": [85, 574, 108, 657], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["う．．．っ？"]}, {"box": [91, 923, 122, 1005], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ぐはっ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-007.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1431, "img_height": 1037, "blocks": [{"box": [1312, 36, 1338, 78], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あ．．．"]}, {"box": [1274, 99, 1295, 150], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["くっ．．．"]}, {"box": [1182, 190, 1204, 296], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ちくしょう．．．"]}, {"box": [781, 188, 830, 291], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ちくしょう", "ちくしょうっ"]}, {"box": [1299, 354, 1321, 497], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ちくしょうッ"]}, {"box": [827, 410, 853, 517], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["トウジッ"]}, {"box": [86, 568, 133, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["仕事ができれば", "問題ないわ"]}, {"box": [306, 867, 377, 939], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["もう", "起きて", "いいの？"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-008.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1437, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1317, 42, 1364, 181], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["この非常時に", "休んでられない．．．か"]}, {"box": [1074, 40, 1124, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["シンジ君は？"]}, {"box": [985, 57, 1011, 112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["病院よ"]}, {"box": [829, 230, 860, 290], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あの後"]}, {"box": [778, 284, 819, 423], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["レーザーカッターで", "非常ハッチを切断"]}, {"box": [1278, 474, 1325, 586], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["強制排除", "されたらしいわ"]}, {"box": [1042, 700, 1066, 780], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["参ったわね"]}, {"box": [770, 868, 819, 948], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["今度ばかり", "は．．．．．"]}, {"box": [530, 49, 575, 145], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["タメかも", "しれないわね"]}, {"box": [234, 56, 513, 141], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["第", "一脳神経", "１９１０月ＡＮＡＬＮＥＲ"]}, {"box": [345, 179, 432, 220], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["「第２５条"]}, {"box": [559, 266, 634, 363], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["きっとなか", "立ち直れない", "わよ"]}, {"box": [475, 349, 515, 363], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["コースタイル"]}, {"box": [376, 366, 449, 392], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["放射線１０万円くらいですね", "Ｑ．リンドサイズは"]}, {"box": [89, 338, 178, 465], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あたしや", "あんたと違って", "神経細そうだもん", "あのバカは"]}, {"box": [583, 625, 660, 740], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ずっと眠り", "続けているわね", "碇君．．．"]}, {"box": [319, 630, 364, 708], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ケガはして", "ないんだし"]}, {"box": [81, 635, 123, 715], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そのうち", "気づくわよ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-009.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1451, "img_height": 1034, "blocks": [{"box": [1265, 38, 1312, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["今頃夢でも", "見てるんじゃないの？"]}, {"box": [1299, 392, 1334, 461], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["碇くん"]}, {"box": [1164, 315, 1196, 376], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["碇くん"]}, {"box": [1017, 385, 1045, 443], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["起きて"]}, {"box": [1322, 664, 1341, 736], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["だれ．．．？"]}, {"box": [977, 667, 997, 736], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["わたしよ"]}, {"box": [796, 869, 823, 940], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["委員長？"]}, {"box": [590, 38, 614, 141], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["鈴原くんは？"]}, {"box": [128, 55, 181, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["鈴原くんは", "どこにいるの？"]}, {"box": [505, 253, 610, 361], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["せっかく", "生懸命", "お弁当作った", "のに"]}, {"box": [626, 439, 657, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["碇くん"]}, {"box": [87, 305, 136, 382], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["どこにも", "いないの"]}, {"box": [532, 519, 561, 609], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["鈴原くんを"]}, {"box": [449, 650, 469, 737], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["僕じゃない"]}, {"box": [340, 658, 413, 749], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["トウジを", "殺したのは", "僕じゃない"]}, {"box": [110, 505, 141, 566], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["返して"]}, {"box": [158, 658, 178, 745], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["殺した．．．？"]}, {"box": [90, 725, 138, 817], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["鈴原くん", "死んだの？"]}, {"box": [539, 907, 563, 978], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ちが．．．う"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-010.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1441, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1329, 32, 1362, 156], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["僕しゃない！"]}, {"box": [857, 50, 911, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["僕はやめてって", "言ったのに"]}, {"box": [806, 133, 833, 257], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["父さんが．．．！"]}, {"box": [1228, 285, 1333, 433], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["父さんが", "トウシを", "殺したんだ！！"]}, {"box": [427, 73, 476, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["気がついた", "みたいだな"]}, {"box": [379, 430, 405, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["加持さん．．．"]}, {"box": [70, 429, 120, 510], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["起き上が", "れるかい？"]}, {"box": [481, 552, 554, 650], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["司令が", "君に会いたい", "そうだ"]}, {"box": [132, 609, 177, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["気はすすまない", "だろうが"]}, {"box": [87, 772, 154, 901], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["意識が戻りしたい", "這ってでも来る", "ようにとの仰せだ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-011.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1434, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1130, 734, 1179, 831], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["思ったより", "元気そうだな"]}, {"box": [1323, 806, 1348, 856], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["カチャ"]}, {"box": [1180, 822, 1220, 891], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["カチャチァ"]}, {"box": [773, 855, 787, 918], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["さて．．"]}, {"box": [595, 55, 620, 120], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["命令違反"]}, {"box": [387, 50, 434, 116], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["エヴァのしてきせん？", "私的占有"]}, {"box": [47, 69, 116, 152], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["それによる", "本部施設の", "一部破壊"]}, {"box": [64, 373, 110, 467], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["これらは全て", "犯罪行為だ"]}, {"box": [618, 566, 666, 677], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["何か言いたい", "ことはあるか？"]}, {"box": [158, 558, 206, 702], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["僕に言いたいことが", "あるんじゃないの？"]}, {"box": [316, 842, 368, 899], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["父さん", "こそ．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-012.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1441, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1352, 71, 1376, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["何のことだ？"]}, {"box": [1149, 237, 1227, 336], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["今質問", "しているのは", "私だ"]}, {"box": [1284, 699, 1369, 868], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["シンジ君ッ！"]}, {"box": [626, 249, 647, 301], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["よせっ"]}, {"box": [230, 296, 273, 350], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["放せ"]}, {"box": [343, 503, 422, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そんな事を", "しても", "何もならない"]}, {"box": [435, 651, 459, 739], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["僕はもう．．．"]}, {"box": [253, 652, 302, 775], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["もうエヴァには", "乗れない"]}, {"box": [78, 543, 113, 627], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["放せよッ"]}, {"box": [503, 880, 528, 960], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["はあっ"]}, {"box": [329, 889, 395, 991], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["エヴァには", "乗りたくない"]}, {"box": [56, 887, 105, 993], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ここにも", "居たくない！"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-013.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1427, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1261, 37, 1324, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["もう父さんの顔は", "二度と見たくない！！！"]}, {"box": [1314, 296, 1333, 351], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["うう．．．"]}, {"box": [1017, 419, 1032, 471], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["くっ．．．"]}, {"box": [1330, 532, 1350, 597], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["わかった"]}, {"box": [969, 550, 1011, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おまえには", "失望した"]}, {"box": [1229, 847, 1273, 915], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ならば", "出て行け"]}, {"box": [614, 51, 663, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["もと居た所へ", "戻れ"]}, {"box": [480, 373, 555, 501], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["望み通り", "二度と会うことも", "あるまい"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-014.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1024, "blocks": [{"box": [900, 35, 931, 94], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["チャッ"]}, {"box": [1277, 362, 1324, 514], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["サード・チルドレンは", "抹消"]}, {"box": [964, 232, 979, 321], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [763, 244, 796, 287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["私だ"]}, {"box": [904, 437, 978, 536], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["初号機の", "専属の", "パイロットは"]}, {"box": [803, 803, 869, 944], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["レイをベーシックに", "ダミーブラグを", "バックアップに回せ"]}, {"box": [219, 38, 248, 106], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["長いこと"]}, {"box": [67, 317, 114, 398], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["お世話に", "なりました"]}, {"box": [379, 495, 474, 567], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["もう一度", "考え直す", "つもりは", "ないの？"]}, {"box": [66, 887, 115, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ありま", "せん"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-015.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1427, "img_height": 1031, "blocks": [{"box": [1283, 47, 1331, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["何度聞かれても", "同じです"]}, {"box": [894, 34, 958, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あたしはあなたに", "自分の夢・願い・", "目的を重ねていたわ"]}, {"box": [774, 234, 815, 324], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["いえあたし", "だけじゃない"]}, {"box": [1318, 494, 1367, 561], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["鈴原君の", "ことは"]}, {"box": [1263, 539, 1307, 621], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["悪かったと", "思ってるわ"]}, {"box": [1077, 500, 1100, 605], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["でもシンジ君"]}, {"box": [891, 617, 955, 757], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["それがあなたの", "重荷になってるのが"]}, {"box": [890, 618, 908, 730], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["わかっていても"]}, {"box": [1184, 822, 1277, 982], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どんな言葉で", "取り繕っても", "あなたの心の傷は", "癒せないでしょうけど"]}, {"box": [1049, 785, 1092, 881], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["これだけは", "覚えておいて"]}, {"box": [787, 750, 875, 893], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あたしたちネルフの", "みんなはあなたに", "未来を託すしか", "なかったのよ"]}, {"box": [788, 753, 873, 891], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あたしたちネルフのみんなはあなたに未来を託すしかなかったのよ"]}, {"box": [450, 50, 477, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["人類の平和ですか？"]}, {"box": [253, 62, 301, 172], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["人の命の重さは", "同じなのに？"]}, {"box": [607, 288, 649, 383], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんの", "夢って．．．"]}, {"box": [558, 358, 602, 470], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["願いって", "何なんですか？"]}, {"box": [330, 381, 406, 466], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["人の命を", "踏みつけに", "して？"]}, {"box": [287, 303, 305, 413], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ごめんなさい"]}, {"box": [73, 398, 122, 495], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["勝手な言い分", "だったわね"]}, {"box": [557, 551, 675, 663], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["本部までの", "バスコードと", "あなたの部屋は", "そのままに", "しておくから"]}, {"box": [431, 548, 466, 659], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["僕はもう"]}, {"box": [491, 900, 519, 985], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ムダです"]}, {"box": [85, 858, 156, 993], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["エヴァには", "乗りません"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-016.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [49, 38, 339, 96], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＩＳＴＡＥ－２２）灰色の空"]}, {"box": [1208, 157, 1252, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["さよなら", "ミサトさん"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-017.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1421, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1312, 591, 1354, 685], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんの", "夢って．．．"]}, {"box": [1068, 598, 1117, 698], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["人類の", "平和ですか？"]}, {"box": [1157, 805, 1203, 920], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["願いって", "何なんですか？"]}, {"box": [900, 835, 947, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["人の命を", "踏みつけにして？"]}, {"box": [432, 47, 452, 118], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ミサト．．"]}, {"box": [564, 411, 621, 487], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["母さんを", "頼む"]}, {"box": [240, 277, 285, 365], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["おまえは", "生きるんだ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-018.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1427, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1315, 70, 1339, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["人類の平和か．．．"]}, {"box": [938, 44, 1005, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今まで", "ガムシャラに", "やって来たけど"]}, {"box": [1068, 348, 1095, 413], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["偽善ね．．．"]}, {"box": [780, 186, 805, 361], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あたしの本当の目的は．．．"]}, {"box": [874, 387, 944, 483], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["その目的はたま", "建て前で", "しかなかった"]}, {"box": [1243, 568, 1273, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["お父さん．．．"]}, {"box": [911, 611, 1002, 776], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あなたの仇を", "討ちたいだけ", "なのかもしれない"]}, {"box": [281, 263, 342, 310], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["．．．", "いいんじゃない", "もしもししない", "いいじゃないか"]}, {"box": [639, 510, 659, 571], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ヘンだな"]}, {"box": [528, 561, 574, 660], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["空はあんなに", "青いのに"]}, {"box": [334, 518, 404, 660], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["昨日まで父さんへの", "怒りであんなにももっ", "繋がった胸も"]}, {"box": [91, 603, 164, 715], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今日はもう", "こんなに冷たく", "なってる"]}, {"box": [576, 836, 645, 903], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["何故暗く", "見えるん", "だろう"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-019.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1427, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1340, 41, 1358, 125], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["わかってる"]}, {"box": [1243, 133, 1270, 221], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["その理由は"]}, {"box": [777, 85, 846, 196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ここに来てから", "信じられない", "事ばかりで"]}, {"box": [1061, 249, 1155, 408], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["僕は泡くってばかりで", "父さんやミサトさんの", "言う事を聞くしか", "できなくて"]}, {"box": [1113, 446, 1157, 557], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["それでも色んな", "人に出会って"]}, {"box": [766, 561, 835, 735], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["閉ざしていたはずの窓が", "知らないうちに開いて", "いたというのに．．．"]}, {"box": [1266, 751, 1342, 892], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["僕が心の中にある", "窓をまた閉じて", "しまったからな"]}, {"box": [620, 54, 664, 118], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ごめん", "トウジ．．．"]}, {"box": [422, 299, 469, 396], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今はもう", "涙も出ない．．．"]}, {"box": [582, 474, 685, 614], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["只今", "東海地方を中心に", "非常事態宣言が", "発令されました"]}, {"box": [211, 507, 390, 609], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ａ特別急行列車Ｒ－１３", "１３：３８発・新厚木行"]}, {"box": [500, 777, 605, 902], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["住民の皆様は", "速やかに指定の", "シェルターへ", "避難して下さい"]}, {"box": [167, 761, 404, 889], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["避難通路"]}, {"box": [153, 856, 384, 966], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.5, "lines": ["ＥＭＥＲＧＥＮＯＹ", "ＰＡＳＳＡＧＥ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-020.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1404, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [769, 178, 799, 263], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["使徒だ．．．"]}, {"box": [1269, 308, 1330, 413], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["総員第一種", "戦闘配置／"]}, {"box": [777, 587, 842, 712], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["地対空迎撃戦", "用意！！"]}, {"box": [1295, 745, 1327, 830], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["目標は？"]}, {"box": [763, 863, 826, 973], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["現在", "侵攻中です"]}, {"box": [570, 63, 632, 206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["駒ヶ岳防衛線", "突破されました"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-021.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [575, 607, 669, 733], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["第１から", "１８番装甲まで", "損壊！"]}, {"box": [307, 618, 376, 709], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["１８もある", "特殊装甲を", "一瞬で．．．！？"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-022.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [976, 101, 1051, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["エヴァの", "地上迎撃は", "間に合わないわ！"]}, {"box": [795, 81, 897, 228], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["アスカには目標が", "ジオフロント内に", "侵入した瞬間を", "狙い撃ちさせて！"]}, {"box": [1258, 303, 1336, 439], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["弐号機を", "ジオフロント内に", "配置！"]}, {"box": [1007, 629, 1061, 735], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["本部施設の", "直接に回して"]}, {"box": [640, 98, 662, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["零号機は！？"]}, {"box": [267, 87, 317, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["左腕の再生が", "まだなのよ"]}, {"box": [581, 478, 629, 573], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["レイはしょうか", "初号機で出せ"]}, {"box": [361, 299, 427, 423], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["Ａ・Ｔ・フィールド", "中和地点に配置", "されています！"]}, {"box": [85, 285, 134, 354], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["戦闘は", "無理．．．か"]}, {"box": [607, 694, 677, 831], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ダミーブラグを", "バックアップとして", "用意"]}, {"box": [93, 725, 114, 779], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["．．．はい"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-023.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1404, "img_height": 1041, "blocks": [{"box": [415, 64, 445, 123], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["僕は．．．"]}, {"box": [75, 57, 124, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["もう乗らないって", "決めたんだ．．．"]}, {"box": [325, 507, 337, 556], "vertical": true, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-024.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1126, 370, 1172, 496], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["何してる？", "こんなところで、"]}, {"box": [1070, 406, 1090, 545], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["避難しないのか．．．"]}, {"box": [1110, 596, 1166, 682], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんで", "ここに！"]}, {"box": [1284, 872, 1347, 945], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["加持", "さん！？"]}, {"box": [751, 864, 824, 1003], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["えーっと", "ここから一番近い", "シェルターはっと"]}, {"box": [607, 64, 658, 185], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["連れ戻しに", "来たんですか？"]}, {"box": [218, 74, 245, 115], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["いや"]}, {"box": [471, 296, 547, 406], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["父さ．．．", "あの人の", "命令ですか！？"]}, {"box": [71, 312, 98, 401], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["俺の意志だ"]}, {"box": [570, 457, 662, 600], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["謀報部に", "見つからないように", "ここまで来るのにも", "苦労したよ"]}, {"box": [300, 458, 391, 623], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["でもこうでもしないと", "君と話すチャンスは", "もう二度とないかも", "しれないからな"]}, {"box": [353, 725, 406, 800], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["話！？", "何です？"]}, {"box": [432, 867, 524, 964], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["君も知って", "るだろ？", "最近監視が", "キビしいんだ"]}, {"box": [74, 861, 149, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["僕は話す事", "なんか", "ありません"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-025.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1085, 12, 1157, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["１５年前", "セカンド・インパクトが", "起きたあの年．．"]}, {"box": [780, 450, 831, 556], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["俺は君と同じ", "１４歳だった"]}, {"box": [1247, 641, 1339, 769], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["俺は君に", "少し感情移入", "しすぎてるのかも", "しれんな"]}, {"box": [46, 54, 251, 87], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＧＥ４３『学門"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-026.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1404, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [771, 450, 825, 553], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["エントリー", "スタート"]}, {"box": [1257, 615, 1288, 739], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ＬＣＬ電過／"]}, {"box": [767, 861, 836, 975], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["Ａ神経", "接続開始！！"]}, {"box": [85, 211, 117, 289], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["うッ．．．"]}, {"box": [585, 328, 616, 474], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["パルス逆流！"]}, {"box": [567, 531, 671, 622], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["初号機", "神経接続を", "拒絶して", "います！"]}, {"box": [430, 531, 478, 619], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まさか", "そんな"]}, {"box": [364, 539, 397, 565], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["碇"]}, {"box": [79, 638, 98, 689], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ああ．．．"]}, {"box": [344, 756, 398, 861], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["私を拒絶する", "つもりか"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-027.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1037, "blocks": [{"box": [1315, 44, 1351, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["起動中止！"]}, {"box": [1094, 66, 1112, 168], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["だめなのね．．．"]}, {"box": [1267, 407, 1335, 486], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["レイはどころか", "零号機で", "出撃させろ"]}, {"box": [1148, 394, 1219, 505], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["初号機は", "ダミーフラクで", "再起動だ"]}, {"box": [982, 394, 999, 497], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["かまいません"]}, {"box": [990, 738, 1016, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["行きます"]}, {"box": [760, 614, 785, 669], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["レイ？"]}, {"box": [1053, 839, 1121, 898], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["しかしどこうか", "零号機", "は．．．"]}, {"box": [635, 62, 662, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["私が死んでも．．．"]}, {"box": [82, 171, 129, 245], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["代わりは", "いるもの"]}, {"box": [588, 305, 664, 411], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あと一撃です", "全ての装甲は", "突破されます"]}, {"box": [643, 503, 667, 590], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["頼んだわよ"]}, {"box": [504, 879, 528, 947], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["アスカ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-028.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1411, "img_height": 1031, "blocks": [{"box": [772, 813, 828, 938], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["おいで", "なすったわね"]}, {"box": [622, 383, 665, 484], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["シンジなんか", "いなくたって"]}, {"box": [607, 596, 687, 792], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["お茶の子", "サイサイよッ！！"]}, {"box": [79, 478, 143, 560], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あんなの", "あたし", "ひとりで．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-029.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1381, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [591, 41, 657, 136], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["地響きが", "激しくなった", "ダカする．．．"]}, {"box": [320, 400, 391, 499], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["使徒は", "どうなったん", "だろう"]}, {"box": [236, 567, 254, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ここは．．．？"]}, {"box": [29, 868, 142, 1023], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なーに", "ネルフは民間人の", "知らない施設を", "いっぱい持ってるって", "ことさ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-030.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1394, "img_height": 1037, "blocks": [{"box": [1168, 50, 1327, 190], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そこらの", "シェルターより断然", "造りがいい．．．", "リニアレールで", "ジオフロントまでの", "アクセスもばっちり", "だしね"]}, {"box": [729, 65, 799, 160], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["駅の地下に", "こんなトコが", "あるなんて．．．"]}, {"box": [1251, 238, 1321, 349], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["非常用食料．．．", "こんなに", "いっぱい"]}, {"box": [992, 250, 1012, 300], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["さてと"]}, {"box": [869, 242, 959, 370], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["俺がネルフを", "スパイしてる", "理由をまだ君に", "教えてなかったな"]}, {"box": [1049, 689, 1119, 758], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["別に興味", "ないです", "けど？"]}, {"box": [785, 702, 829, 798], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["まあ", "そういうなよ"]}, {"box": [729, 698, 765, 801], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ミもフタも", "ないだろう．．．"]}, {"box": [626, 29, 650, 96], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["すべては"]}, {"box": [566, 50, 607, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["セカンド・インバクトが", "きっかけだった．．．"]}, {"box": [76, 77, 121, 218], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あれが起きた直後は", "ひどい有様だったよ"]}, {"box": [605, 303, 655, 385], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["想像できる", "かい？"]}, {"box": [458, 285, 482, 378], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["都市は壊滅し"]}, {"box": [366, 424, 383, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["人は住む場所もなく"]}, {"box": [120, 317, 164, 455], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["数えきれないほどの", "人が死んだ"]}, {"box": [645, 635, 667, 777], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["俺の両親も死んだよ"]}, {"box": [321, 474, 336, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["食料は不足し"]}, {"box": [191, 628, 258, 770], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["その頃はそうした", "親を亡くした子供が", "ごろごろしてた"]}, {"box": [495, 826, 541, 953], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["俺と４つ下の", "弟だけが残された"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-031.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1401, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1273, 53, 1316, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["だがそんな子供たちを", "放ってはおけんだろ？"]}, {"box": [1175, 113, 1243, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["国はそうした子を", "手当たり次第に", "集めて"]}, {"box": [762, 146, 811, 227], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["変護施設に", "放り込んだ"]}, {"box": [1303, 322, 1349, 406], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["だが", "考えてみろ"]}, {"box": [1157, 437, 1199, 578], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["国中に何十万という", "孤児がいるんだ"]}, {"box": [959, 322, 1052, 450], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["世話人の数も", "足りないから", "規律だけはいい？", "異常に厳しくてな"]}, {"box": [743, 326, 756, 389], "vertical": true, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [1106, 499, 1146, 640], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["小さな施設はすぐに", "ハンク状態さ"]}, {"box": [986, 493, 1055, 607], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["スパイの話", "じゃなかったん", "ですか？"]}, {"box": [993, 714, 1060, 841], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["とにかく", "ガマンができなく", "なって"]}, {"box": [740, 493, 827, 578], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．", "悪かったな", "前フリな", "長くて．．．"]}, {"box": [747, 719, 815, 816], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["俺と弟と", "他に仲間を", "５人連れてな"]}, {"box": [1197, 764, 1291, 878], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["食料も衣類も", "不足して", "寝る場所だって", "奪い合いだ"]}, {"box": [942, 753, 990, 825], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["俺たちはだった？", "脱走した"]}, {"box": [603, 71, 664, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["そんでもって", "後はお決まりの", "コースさ"]}, {"box": [347, 65, 394, 142], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["お決まりっ", "て？"]}, {"box": [227, 65, 320, 160], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["スパイの前は", "ドロボウ", "だったんです", "か？"]}, {"box": [65, 62, 176, 142], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そうでも", "しなきゃ", "生きてけ", "なかったっ", "てんだよ"]}, {"box": [339, 384, 427, 509], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["わかるだろう？", "食うためには", "ドロボウとか", "ひったくりとか．．．"]}, {"box": [181, 290, 321, 394], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["だが世界中が", "飢えてる時に", "そうそう", "食う物が", "手に入るワケ", "じゃない"]}, {"box": [68, 303, 136, 383], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そんな時", "偶然見つけ", "たのが．．．"]}, {"box": [541, 619, 637, 692], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["丁度ここ", "みたいな", "軍の食料", "倉庫さ"]}, {"box": [324, 593, 462, 719], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["今みたいに", "管理システムが", "しっかりしてた", "ワケじゃないから", "忍び込むのは", "簡単だった"]}, {"box": [54, 595, 126, 704], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ハラが減る度に", "何度も足を", "運んだよ"]}, {"box": [61, 862, 157, 975], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["全員で", "動くといだ", "目立つから", "当番を決めてな"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-032.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1391, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1291, 55, 1316, 108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そして"]}, {"box": [1074, 63, 1118, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あの日は俺が", "当番だった"]}, {"box": [1289, 263, 1331, 419], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["だれだ！？"]}, {"box": [1255, 532, 1325, 655], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["誰かそこに", "いるのは", "判ってるんだ！！"]}, {"box": [1206, 555, 1225, 642], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おとなしく"]}, {"box": [1080, 839, 1110, 975], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["出てこい！！"]}, {"box": [653, 323, 667, 355], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["フン"]}, {"box": [52, 396, 123, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あうっ"]}, {"box": [650, 547, 675, 611], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["げほッ"]}, {"box": [622, 596, 647, 659], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["げほッ"]}, {"box": [328, 553, 375, 708], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["最近この辺を", "うろついてるガキだな"]}, {"box": [327, 873, 395, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["さんざんボの", "倉庫を荒らし", "やがって"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-033.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1401, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1268, 75, 1318, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["他の仲間は", "どうした？"]}, {"box": [1008, 39, 1105, 128], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["さあ！", "オマエらの", "住みかを", "教えるんだ"]}, {"box": [918, 72, 942, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["な．．．何の事だよ"]}, {"box": [985, 276, 1056, 451], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["オマエらみたいな", "雪虫はまとめて", "施設にフチこんでやる"]}, {"box": [755, 310, 862, 439], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["仲間なんて", "いねえよ", "俺．．．", "ひとりだよ"]}, {"box": [1225, 469, 1331, 591], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["へかむ", "すぐさんし", "体がし"]}, {"box": [1217, 756, 1336, 883], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いつも", "仲間と", "つるんでるの", "知ってるゾ"]}, {"box": [735, 852, 816, 997], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おとなしく", "仲間の居場所を", "はくんだよ！！"]}, {"box": [398, 65, 481, 158], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ちっ", "しぶとい", "ガキだぜ"]}, {"box": [342, 79, 369, 120], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["おい"]}, {"box": [77, 75, 179, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オマエ", "自分の立場", "わかってん", "のか？"]}, {"box": [618, 398, 663, 499], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["いいか？", "オレたちはな"]}, {"box": [496, 425, 600, 521], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["勝手に", "軍の施設に", "入りこんだ", "ヤツを"]}, {"box": [80, 421, 160, 529], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["殺してもいい", "事になってん", "だよ"]}, {"box": [570, 606, 673, 747], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["つまり今ここで", "オマエを殺しても", "かまわないって", "事だ"]}, {"box": [314, 606, 339, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ぼうや"]}, {"box": [73, 901, 129, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["チャンスを", "やろう"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-034.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1394, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1240, 73, 1289, 194], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["仲間の居場所を", "教えたら"]}, {"box": [1181, 141, 1230, 230], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["オマエは", "助けてやる"]}, {"box": [754, 164, 799, 253], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["だがそうで", "ないなら．．．"]}, {"box": [1174, 483, 1268, 611], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["今すぐ", "この引き金を", "引く．．．"]}, {"box": [598, 70, 652, 144], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["俺はね", "シンジ君"]}, {"box": [413, 58, 463, 133], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["死ぬのが", "怖かった"]}, {"box": [91, 141, 168, 314], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["今まで生きて来て", "あれほど怖かった事は", "他になかったよ"]}, {"box": [631, 592, 675, 695], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["しゃべったん", "ですか．．．？"]}, {"box": [232, 587, 249, 656], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["それから"]}, {"box": [83, 865, 130, 970], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どうなったん", "です．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-035.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1394, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1204, 36, 1256, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．東の共同墓地と", "国道の間の．．．"]}, {"box": [758, 107, 785, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["廃ヒル．．．"]}, {"box": [1281, 279, 1306, 319], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ＯＫ"]}, {"box": [1159, 439, 1180, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["いいコだ"]}, {"box": [1064, 280, 1114, 358], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["行くぞ", "おまえら"]}, {"box": [871, 284, 946, 373], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おまえは", "その小僧を", "見張ってろ"]}, {"box": [722, 289, 738, 324], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ＱＫ"]}, {"box": [1022, 574, 1093, 697], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．というワケだ", "仲よくお留守番", "しようぜ"]}, {"box": [628, 303, 654, 424], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["このガキ．．．"]}, {"box": [560, 398, 596, 475], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["待てっ"]}, {"box": [491, 649, 509, 690], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["はあ"]}, {"box": [378, 551, 422, 609], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はっ"]}, {"box": [598, 766, 617, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["はあ"]}, {"box": [361, 745, 416, 831], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はあっ"]}, {"box": [45, 927, 102, 1013], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はあ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-036.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1391, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1248, 48, 1278, 108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["はあ"]}, {"box": [1203, 97, 1232, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["はあ"]}, {"box": [1251, 247, 1303, 369], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["俺が仲間の所に", "戻った時"]}, {"box": [760, 363, 836, 556], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["丁度軍のトラックが", "逃げるように", "去って行くところだった"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-037.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1397, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1252, 447, 1316, 594], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["弟と仲間の命を", "犠牲にして"]}, {"box": [986, 756, 1047, 928], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["俺は", "生き残ったんだよ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-038.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1054, "blocks": [{"box": [1170, 20, 1320, 305], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["サイチャンプに"]}, {"box": [1238, 809, 1336, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["カチッ", "カチッ"]}, {"box": [754, 828, 799, 895], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["くっ"]}, {"box": [627, 64, 669, 126], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["次っ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-039.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [944, 71, 1023, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ＡＴ：フィールドは", "中和してるハズ", "なのにィ"]}, {"box": [1242, 378, 1329, 462], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["なんで", "平気なの", "よッ"]}, {"box": [1273, 704, 1368, 955], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["こぉんのォォォ", "オオオォオ"]}, {"box": [626, 254, 677, 375], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["弟と仲間の命を", "代償にして"]}, {"box": [272, 249, 370, 355], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["もちろん", "その後は", "激しい後悔の", "嵐だったよ"]}, {"box": [418, 595, 471, 669], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["俺は生き", "残った．．"]}, {"box": [280, 635, 336, 743], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["自ら死ぬこと", "さえ考えた"]}, {"box": [113, 794, 175, 947], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["が", "こうも思った"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-040.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1273, 46, 1319, 193], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["セカンド・インバクト", "さえなければ"]}, {"box": [875, 60, 895, 140], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["それからさ"]}, {"box": [1126, 306, 1199, 403], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["弟は死なずに", "すんだんじゃ", "ないかってね"]}, {"box": [741, 247, 787, 445], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["俺がセカンドインパクトの", "正体を追いかけ始めたのは"]}, {"box": [1246, 485, 1338, 597], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["政府の流した", "巨大隕石落下の", "情報は信憑性に", "欠けていたし"]}, {"box": [1019, 568, 1085, 680], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もし裏で糸を", "引いてる連中が", "いたとしたら"]}, {"box": [982, 610, 1003, 722], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["許しておけない"]}, {"box": [899, 491, 942, 655], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["セカンド・インバクトの", "正体を突き止めるのが"]}, {"box": [1051, 834, 1122, 961], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["もう二度と弟たち", "みたいな犠牲者を", "出しちゃいけない"]}, {"box": [758, 810, 807, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["弟に対する俺の", "償いたと思ったんだ"]}, {"box": [546, 71, 663, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["幸い俺はしんくっ", "遠い親戚に", "引き取られて", "大学にも", "行かせてもらい"]}, {"box": [432, 82, 478, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["色々と", "勉強もした"]}, {"box": [313, 72, 352, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["スパイになる", "ための．．．？"]}, {"box": [81, 74, 101, 123], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まあね"]}, {"box": [299, 327, 347, 394], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そんな時", "だったよ"]}, {"box": [593, 527, 641, 625], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["葛城に", "出会ったのは"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-041.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1411, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1300, 23, 1343, 132], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["俺たちはすぐに", "恋に落ちた"]}, {"box": [1111, 118, 1134, 198], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["幸せだった"]}, {"box": [967, 48, 1018, 129], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["幸せに溺れ", "すぎて"]}, {"box": [1088, 388, 1113, 411], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["が"]}, {"box": [777, 298, 825, 393], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ある日恐怖に", "襲われた"]}, {"box": [1267, 490, 1315, 569], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["俺は弟を", "殺したのに"]}, {"box": [1038, 692, 1087, 819], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["それが別れた", "理由なんですか？"]}, {"box": [767, 515, 866, 640], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["自分だけが", "こんなに幸せで", "いいんだろうかっ", "てね"]}, {"box": [758, 691, 828, 836], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["それ以上", "恋にのめり込めなく", "なっただけさ"]}, {"box": [1145, 838, 1164, 903], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["そんな．．．"]}, {"box": [635, 78, 672, 184], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんが", "かわいそうです"]}, {"box": [414, 61, 436, 100], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["でも"]}, {"box": [497, 312, 559, 468], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんは．．．", "今でも加持さんのこと", "好きなんだと思います"]}, {"box": [347, 363, 414, 490], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["好きでも", "どうしようもない", "ことがあるって．．．"]}, {"box": [219, 250, 276, 326], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["同じ", "なんだよ"]}, {"box": [104, 377, 137, 439], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["葛城も"]}, {"box": [611, 599, 635, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え？"]}, {"box": [172, 571, 261, 797], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["彼女は南極でその日", "セカンド・インバクトに遭遇した", "調査隊のただひとりの", "生き残りなんだよ"]}, {"box": [93, 789, 158, 968], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["“セカンド・インバクトを", "間近で見た", "ただひとりの人間さ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-042.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1401, "img_height": 1047, "blocks": [{"box": [1261, 41, 1325, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["南極で発見された", "「アダム」と呼ばれる", "物体の調査"]}, {"box": [1176, 88, 1217, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["彼女の父親はその", "指揮を執っていた"]}, {"box": [923, 71, 995, 197], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あいつの父親は", "あいつをかばって", "死に"]}, {"box": [755, 199, 797, 281], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あいつはい？", "生き残った"]}, {"box": [1050, 320, 1097, 433], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そしてその最中", "起こった大爆発"]}, {"box": [1240, 522, 1338, 650], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["もちろんその事は", "あいつの心と体に", "大きな傷跡として", "残った"]}, {"box": [1299, 706, 1351, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["俺たちは", "２人とも"]}, {"box": [759, 522, 847, 665], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あいつがネルフに", "はいったのも", "その事と少なからず", "関係があるんだろう"]}, {"box": [881, 737, 905, 795], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["そして"]}, {"box": [980, 893, 1055, 1014], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["幸せになっては", "いけない", "運命なんだよ"]}, {"box": [767, 867, 798, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["シンジ君"]}, {"box": [571, 128, 607, 235], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["君も同じだ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-043.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1044, "blocks": [{"box": [1040, 305, 1108, 379], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["！！"]}, {"box": [754, 428, 809, 495], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["なに", "あれ？"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-044.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1351, 451, 1389, 522], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ひ．．．"]}, {"box": [1017, 483, 1066, 774], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ああぁあああ"]}, {"box": [1119, 864, 1157, 934], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ．．．"]}, {"box": [770, 854, 803, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["あっ．．．あ．．．"]}, {"box": [352, 74, 372, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["くうっ"]}, {"box": [256, 473, 298, 622], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["アスカッ"]}, {"box": [524, 736, 694, 1051], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["みヰヰヶへヘけさ"]}, {"box": [96, 843, 127, 979], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["やめなさい"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-045.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1404, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1260, 34, 1332, 143], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["全神経", "カット！"]}, {"box": [774, 139, 818, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["急いで！"]}, {"box": [582, 35, 608, 137], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["僕も同じって"]}, {"box": [124, 100, 172, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どういう", "ことですか．．．？"]}, {"box": [638, 263, 659, 367], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ひょっとして"]}, {"box": [398, 258, 453, 416], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あれは僕のせいじゃ", "ない"]}, {"box": [86, 271, 132, 350], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["父さんが", "やったんだ"]}, {"box": [398, 458, 448, 615], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["父さんのせいで", "トウジは死んだんだ"]}, {"box": [202, 691, 227, 779], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そして君は"]}, {"box": [508, 823, 584, 915], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["トウジの事", "言ってるん", "ですか．．．？"]}, {"box": [61, 853, 113, 957], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ただ見ていた", "だけだった"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-046.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1414, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [832, 81, 963, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["タミーシステムに", "切り替わる前に", "君が戦っていれば", "あるいは使徒を倒し", "鈴原君を助けられた", "かもしれない"]}, {"box": [1122, 295, 1174, 451], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["君は闘おうと思えば", "聞えたはずだ"]}, {"box": [827, 323, 849, 360], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["だが"]}, {"box": [763, 360, 807, 443], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["君はそれを", "しなかった"]}, {"box": [1241, 541, 1292, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["鈴原君は", "死に"]}, {"box": [1046, 527, 1111, 652], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["俺が弟の命を", "代償にして", "生き残ったように"]}, {"box": [926, 581, 991, 708], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["葛城が父親の命を", "犠牲にして", "生き残ったように"]}, {"box": [1244, 851, 1293, 939], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["君は", "生き残った"]}, {"box": [903, 791, 918, 884], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["鈴原君の命は"]}, {"box": [805, 826, 872, 954], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["君の血や肉となり", "君の命の中に", "取り込まれたんだ"]}, {"box": [524, 17, 599, 154], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["それでも", "何もなかったかの", "ように"]}, {"box": [124, 203, 174, 324], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["君は生きて", "いけるのかい？"]}, {"box": [608, 889, 640, 956], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["僕は．．"]}, {"box": [95, 808, 147, 974], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どうすれば", "いいんですか．．．？"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-047.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1411, "img_height": 1051, "blocks": [{"box": [1048, 26, 1118, 198], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["この通路の奥の", "リニアシューターＲ１８で", "ジオフロントに戻れる"]}, {"box": [1259, 428, 1304, 522], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["だが前にも", "言ったはずだ"]}, {"box": [785, 228, 856, 326], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それに乗るか", "乗らないかは", "君の自由だ"]}, {"box": [766, 438, 837, 550], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["真実から", "目をそらしては", "いけない"]}, {"box": [1237, 595, 1330, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["使徒がネルフの地下に眠る", "アダムと接触すれば", "サード・インパクトが", "起こると言われている"]}, {"box": [884, 687, 934, 847], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["今度は人類の命の", "全てが奪われるだろう"]}, {"box": [774, 836, 821, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["それを", "止められるのは"]}, {"box": [611, 75, 671, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["使徒と同じ", "力を持つ"]}, {"box": [399, 316, 457, 480], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["エヴァンゲリオン", "だけだ"]}], "img_path": "EVA7-048.JPG"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1407, "img_height": 1041, "blocks": [{"box": [945, 20, 994, 96], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ちゃんと", "ある．．．"]}, {"box": [1250, 365, 1331, 530], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["弐号機大破！", "戦闘不能！"]}, {"box": [1140, 384, 1162, 495], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["キャーーー"]}, {"box": [952, 388, 1073, 413], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [748, 204, 794, 344], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ちゃんと", "ついてるわよね"]}, {"box": [799, 388, 819, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [1319, 668, 1338, 771], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["アスカは！？"]}, {"box": [1018, 692, 1052, 741], "ve